      "s": "« » meaning 'to forget' is used generally, regardless of the reason—whether due to negligence, abandonment of restraint, or anything else (24 verses: 2:106, 2:286, 6:68, 7:51, 9:67, 12:42, 18:24, 18:57, 18:61, 18:63, 18:73, 19:23, 19:64, 20:52, 20:88, 20:115, 20:126, 32:14, 36:78, 39:8, 45:34, 58:19, 59:19, 87:6)",
      "d": "«نَسِیَ» «وَ ضَرَبَ لَنَا مَثَلًا وَّ نَسِیَ خَلۡقَہٗ» «اَنْسٰی» «فَاَنۡسٰہُ الشَّیۡطٰنُ ذِکۡرَ رَبِّہٖ»"
    },
    {
