      "d": "«اَشَدُّ» «قُوَّۃً فِیْ شَیْءٍ»\nFor example: The Noble Quran says:\n«یُرَدُّوۡنَ اِلٰۤی اَشَدِّ الۡعَذَابِ»\nTranslation: They will be returned to the more severe punishment."
