      "s": "« » Increasing at every moment (1 verse: 69:10)",
      "d": "«رَبَا ، رَبْوًا» «رَابِیَۃ»\nFor example: The Noble Quran says:\n«فَعَصَوۡا  رَسُوۡلَ  رَبِّہِمۡ  فَاَخَذَہُمۡ  اَخۡذَۃً  رَّابِیَۃً»\nTranslation: They disobeyed the Messenger of their Lord, so He seized them with a seizure, ever-increasing."
    },
    {
