      "s": "« » basic meaning is to lose the way or to cause to lose the way (163 verses: 1:7-2:16-2:26-2:108-2:175-2:198-2:282-3:69-3:90-3:164-4:44-4:60-4:88-4:113-4:116-4:119-4:136-4:143-4:167-4:176-5:12-5:60-5:77-5:105-6:24-6:39-6:56-6:74-6:77-6:94-6:116-6:117-6:119-6:125-6:140-6:144-7:30-7:37-7:38-7:53-7:60-7:61-7:149-7:155-7:178-7:179-7:186-9:37-9:115-10:30-10:32-10:88-10:108-11:21-12:8-12:30-12:95-13:14-13:27-13:33-14:3-14:18-14:27-14:30-14:36-15:56-16:25-16:36-16:37-16:87-16:93-16:125-17:15-17:67-17:72-17:97-18:17-18:51-18:104-19:38-19:75-20:52-20:79-20:85-20:92-20:123-21:54-22:4-22:9-22:12-23:106-25:17-25:29-25:34-25:42-25:44-26:20-26:86-26:97-26:99-27:81-27:92-28:15-28:50-28:75-28:85-30:29-30:53-31:6-31:11-32:10-33:36-33:67-34:8-34:24-34:50-35:8-36:24-36:47-36:62-37:69-37:71-38:26-39:8-39:22-39:23-39:36-39:37-39:41-40:25-40:33-40:34-40:50-40:74-41:29-41:48-41:52-42:18-42:44-42:46-43:40-45:23-46:5-46:28-46:32-50:27-53:2-53:30-54:24-54:47-56:51-56:92-60:1-62:2-67:9-67:29-68:7-68:26-71:24-71:27-74:31-83:32-93:7)",
