      "h": "To Perish / To Cause to Perish",
      "hw": "ہلاک",
      "s": "« » means to perish, to be destroyed; it is general for both living and non-living things (63 verses: 2:195-2:205-3:117-4:176-5:17-6:6-6:26-6:47-6:131-7:4-7:129-7:155-7:164-7:173-8:42-8:54-9:42-10:13-11:117-12:85-14:13-15:4-17:16-17:17-17:58-18:59-19:74-19:98-20:128-20:134-21:6-21:9-21:95-22:45-23:48-26:139-26:208-27:49-28:43-28:58-28:59-28:78-28:88-29:31-32:26-36:31-38:3-40:34-43:8-44:37-45:24-46:27-46:35-47:13-50:36-53:50-54:51-67:28-69:5-69:6-69:29-77:16-90:6)",
